  <trk>
    <name>Tour de La Seya hike</name>
    <desc>Panoramic route along the ridge between La Seya and Grand Garde above Ovronnaz. The region is famous for its variety of alpine flowers. The ascent is eased by the chairlift – however, the return walk to Ovronnaz through forests and meadows is worthwhile.</desc>
